title: 12/28/21 DPS Best Of  - Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 12/28/21 DPS Best Of  - Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh Guest Hosting
description:
On the Tuesday edition of The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show, Rob and TJ take up for James Harden and how he has adjusted his game with the Nets this season given the new rules. The guys break down the Lakers' season to this point and the issues they have had with star guard Russell Westbrook.

Rob and TJ talk about the Dolphins' Monday Night win over the Saints. Rob is not buying into the Dolphins as a team that can make an impact in the post-season, TJ thinks there are a lot of good things going the Dolphins' way heading down the stretch.

Rob and TJ break down the NFC Playoff picture, and narrow in on how the Cowboys and the Cardinals factor into things.
